@base = http://localhost:3000/jobs

### Get all
GET {{base}}

### Create a new job (success)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_type": "email",
  "payload": {
    "to": "covenantekojoe@gmail.com"
  }
}

### Create a new job (failed)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_type": "email",
  "payload": {
    "to": "test2@gmail.com"
  }
}

### Get a particular job
GET {{base}}/987014b5-10af-4765-af16-15aa7b89dd9f
